name: LEDICONS - 120+ Modern Customizable Icons
description:
What’s LEDICONS?


LEDICONS is a Free Icon Pack For Your Projects & Designs. LEDICONS is designed in Dark Mode & Light Mode in 2 Styles, Regular (Outline) and Duotone. LEDICONS is a modern rounded iconpack for your awesome designs.


More:

  • 120+ Fully Customizable Icons
  • 2 Styles, Regular (Outline) and Duotone
  • 2 Themes, Dark Mode & Light Mode
  • Perfect Pixels and Vectorized
  • Editable and Componented
  • 24px - Standard Grid Size
  • Modern Rounded Style
  • Only For Figma Community
  • Free and Easy For Use
